{"word":"τήκω","slug":"τήκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τήκω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>Root. <el>ΤΑΚ</el>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>in classic Gr. the <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> and plup. <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> are supplied by the <a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>τέτηκα, ἐτετήκειν</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>Act.</a></a> <i>to melt, melt down</i> (<a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a>), of metals, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: <i>to dissipate</i> clouds, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to cause to waste</i> or <i>pine away</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, with <a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>τέτηκα</el>, <i>to be dissolved, melt away</i>, of snow, <i>to thaw</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic; of metals, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>; <el>ἄλφιτα πυρὶ τ.</el> <i>is consumed</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>; of a corpse, <i>to fall away</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>; <el>πῦρ τετακός</el> a <i>dead</i> fire, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to melt</i> or <i>waste away, pine</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic; <el>βλέμμα τηκόμενον</el> a <i>languishing</i> look, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}